node.text:
New Year, New Chalets! 🎆 Our portfolio is ever-expanding to include the finest properties in the Alps. Take a look at some of our latest additions... ❄️
.
📍 Chalet Lupa, Chamonix (1-2)
📍 Chalet Ranch, Verbier (3-4)
📍 Chalet Zaza, Morzine (5-6)
📍 Chalet Joy, Morzine (7-8)
.
To book one of these luxury ski chalets in the Alps, get in touch with our Ski Specialists at ask@skiinluxury.com, or give us a call on +44 (0)1202 203650. Happy New Year! 🌟
.
.
.
